Cli%3EWhen%20billionaires%20come%20visit%20for%20an%20annual%20conference%2C%20his%20sales%20dip%20during%20a%20normally%20busy%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFrehling%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20area%20and%20said%20he's%20never%20met%20a%20local%20who%20is%20excited%20about%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jacob%20Frehling%2C%20the%20co-owner%20of%20Maude's%20Coffee%20and%20Clothes%20in%20Ketchum%2C%20Idaho%2C%20about%20a%20six-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20Lodge.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20seen%20sales%20data%20from%20last%20year%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ethat%20indicate%20Maude's%20saw%20a%20drop%20in%20transactions%20during%20Sun%20Valley%20week%20compared%20to%20the%20week%20immediately%20after%20in%20July.%20Representatives%20for%20the%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20Sun%20Valley%20conference%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lived%20in%20Sun%20Valley%2C%20Idaho%2C%20practically%20my%20entire%20life.%20My%20family%20has%20been%20pretty%20dug%20into%20the%20community%20for%20a%20long%20time%20%E2%80%94%20my%20mom%20owns%20a%20clothing%20store%2C%20my%20cousins%20have%20a%20restaurant%2C%20and%20my%20dad%20used%20to%20run%20a%20restaurant%2C%20too.%20About%20eight%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20opened%20our%20own%20business%3A%20Maude's%20Coffee%20and%20Clothes%2C%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20vintage%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-jets-land-sun-valley-conference-billionaires-ceos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAllen%20%26amp%3B%20Company's%20Sun%20Valley%20Conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20around%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20I%20remember%20some%20of%20my%20friends%20getting%20hired%20as%20nannies%20or%20to%20develop%20photos%2C%20and%20I%20was%20jealous%20of%20their%20opportunity%20to%20make%20an%20easy%20chunk%20of%20money.%20Now%2C%20though%2C%20my%20perspective%20on%20the%20whole%20thing%20is%20a%20little%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20an%20incredible%20local%20following%20at%20Maude's%2C%20but%20this%20whole%20area%20is%20a%20visitor's%20economy.%20Practically%20everyone%20in%20the%20retail%20and%20service%20industries%20relies%20on%20tourists.%20When%20the%20billionaires%20fly%20into%20the%20area%20every%20July%2C%20they%20go%20straight%20to%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20Lodge%20just%20outside%20the%20heart%20of%20Ketchum%20to%20have%20a%20catered%20experience.%20Most%20of%20their%20dollars%20don't%20flow%20back%20into%20town%2C%20unless%20they're%20booking%20out%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jacob%20and%20Maude%20Frehling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d81c83d5881a51c1cea88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221062%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Frehlings%20ran%20a%20food%20truck%20before%20opening%20Maude's.%20Jacob%20Frehling%20said%20employees%20for%20the%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20conference%20took%20a%20picture%20moments%20after%20they%20were%20engaged.%3Cp%3EJacob%20Frehling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20usually%20the%20busiest%20time%20of%20year%20for%20my%20business.%20But%20when%20the%20conference%20comes%2C%20guests%20rent%20out%20tons%20of%20rooms%20and%20book%20all%20the%20fishing%20guides%2C%20outdoor%20adventures%2C%20and%20restaurants.%20Other%20tourists%20can't%20really%20visit%20the%20area%20that%20week.%20The%20Sun%20Valley%20Lodge%20is%20big%3B%20that's%20hundreds%20of%20people%20who%20aren't%20there%20and%20aren't%20circulating%20their%20dollars%20in%20local%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20zero-sum%20game%2C%20but%20my%20number%20of%20sales%20drops%20at%20least%20a%20bit%20every%20year.%20The%20billionaires%20at%20the%20conference%20throw%20a%20weird%20wrench%20in%20the%20cog%20of%20the%20summer%20economy%2C%20stepping%20on%20the%20brakes%20for%20regular%20people%20during%20what%20should%20be%20a%20very%2C%20very%2C%20very%20busy%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20it's%20all%20bad.%20I'm%20sure%20the%20conference%20is%20great%20if%20you're%20directly%20involved%2C%20but%20many%20locals%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20know%20aren't.%20I've%20gotten%20to%20know%20some%20members%20of%20the%20billionaire%20entourage%2C%20like%20dancers%20and%20bodyguards%2C%20who%20come%20each%20year.%20They're%20great%2C%20and%20I%20actually%20always%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20though%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20leave%20town%20during%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20week%2C%20but%20someone%20has%20to%20run%20Maude's.%20I'm%20born%20and%20raised%20here%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20met%20a%20single%20person%20who%20is%20from%20this%20place%20that's%20happy%20when%20the%20jets%20touch%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-sales-sun-valley-allen-company-billionaire-conference-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752154621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d814485e81483682d9964%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-sales-sun-valley-allen-company-billionaire-conference-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jacob%20Frehling%20co-owns%20a%20small%20business%20near%20Sun%20Valley%2C%20but%20the%20annual%20billionaire%20conference%20has%20hurt%20his%20sales%20rather%20than%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22atecotzky%40businessinsider.com%20(Alice%20Tecotzky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-business-sales-sun-valley-allen-company-billion