20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Education%20Above%20All%20Foundation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686e7f9af748d8c055f54014%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Education%20Above%20All%20Foundation%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2F%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENonprofits%20like%20Education%20Above%20All%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20address%20global%20inequities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20initiatives%20align%20with%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20to%20promote%20peace%20and%20prosperity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-everything%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20on%20AI%20adoption%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20millions%20of%20young%20people%20worldwide%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20acquire%20knowledge%20as%20part%20of%20their%20learning%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20complete%20assignments%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20one%20organization%20is%20concerned%20that%20those%20in%20developing%20countries%20without%20access%20to%20the%20tech%20could%20be%20put%20at%20an%20unfair%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20using%20the%20very%20technology%20it%20believes%20is%20causing%20this%20problem%20to%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20Above%20All%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20based%20in%20Qatar%2C%20believes%20that%20because%20most%20of%20the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisc-personality-test-ai-models-openai-chatgpt-gemini-copilot-deepseek-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epopular%20AI%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20created%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20they%20aren't%20equipped%20to%20understand%20the%20linguistic%20and%20ethnic%20nuances%20of%20non-English-speaking%20countries%2C%20creating%20education%20inequities%20on%20a%20global%20scale.%20But%20its%20team%20sees%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20tackle%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202025%2C%20the%20charity%20teamed%20up%20with%20MIT%2C%20Harvard%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%20to%20introduce%20a%20free%20and%20open-source%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-literacy-ethics-teaching-students-educators-scholars-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20program%20called%20Digi-Wise.%20Delivered%20in%20partnership%20with%20educators%20in%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20it%20encourages%20children%20to%20spot%20AI-fueled%20misinformation%2C%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-4-favorite-ai-tools-from-2024-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20responsibly%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%20and%20even%20develop%20their%20own%20AI%20tools%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20charity%20has%20developed%20its%20own%20generative%20AI%20chatbot%20called%20Ferby.%20It%20allows%20users%20to%20access%20and%20personalize%20educational%20resources%20from%20the%20Internet-Free%20Education%20Resource%20Bank%2C%20an%20online%20library%20containing%20hundreds%20of%20free%20and%20open-source%20learning%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20Above%20All%20said%20it's%20already%20being%20used%20by%20over%205%20million%20Indian%20children%20to%20access%20%26quot%3Bproject-based%20learning%26quot%3B%20in%20partnership%20with%20Indian%20nonprofit%20Mantra4Change.%20More%20recently%2C%20Education%20Above%20All%20has%20embedded%20Ferby%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-100-top-6-edtech-education-tech-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eedtech%3C%2Fa%3E%20platform%20SwiftChat%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20124%20million%20students%20and%20teachers%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFerby%20curates%2C%20customizes%2C%20and%20creates%20learning%20materials%20to%20fit%20local%20realities%2C%20so%20a%20teacher%20in%20rural%20Malawi%20can%20run%20the%20right%20science%20experiment%20as%20easily%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%20downtown%20Doha%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aishwarya%20Shetty%2C%20an%20education%20specialist%20at%20Education%20Above%20All.%20%26quot%3BBy%20marrying%20offline%20ingenuity%20with%20AI%20convenience%2C%20we%20make%20learning%20local%2C%20low-resource%2C%20and%20always%20within%20reach%2C%20yet%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEducation%20Above%20All%20is%20among%20a%20group%20of%20organizations%20using%20AI%20to%20tackle%20global%20inequality%20and%20work%20toward%20realizing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsdgs.un.org%2Fgoals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Created%20in%202015%2C%20the%20UN%20SDGs%20comprise%2017%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20environmental%20targets%20that%20serve%20as%20guidelines%20for%20nations%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20individuals%20to%20follow%20to%20help%20achieve%20a%20more%20peaceful%20and%20prosperous%20world.%20Education%20Above%20All's%20projects%20fall%20under%20SDG%204%3A%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e2cc57c-3a86-4652-b418-888b59d4eeda%5C%22%3EA%20global%20effort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20range%20of%20other%20organizations%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20augment%20and%20enhance%20their%20education%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20To%20The%20Rescue%2C%20a%20global%20nonprofit%20that%20connects%20charities%20with%20pro-bono%20software%20development%20teams%20to%20meet%20their%20goals%2C%20is%20another%20organization%20using%20AI%20in%20support%20of%20the%20UN%20SDGs.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20three-year%20AI-for-good%20accelerator%20program%20to%20help%20NGOs%20meet%20the%20various%20UN%20SDGs%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20organization%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20program%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmercy-corps-generative-ai-tool-humanitarian-aid-workers-field-information-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMercy%20Corps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20humanitarian%20group%20that%20works%20across%20over%2040%20countries%20to%20tackle%20crises%20like%20poverty%2C%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20natural%20disasters%2C%20and%20violence.%20Through%20the%20accelerator%2C%20it%20created%20an%20AI%20strategy%20tool%20that%20helps%20first%20responders%20predict%20disasters%20and%20coordinate%20resources.%20The%20World%20Institute%20on%20Disability%20AI%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20accelerator%20program%2C%20creating%20a%20resource-matching%20system%20that%20helps%20organizations%20allocate%20support%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities%20in%20hours%20rather%20than%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20International%20Telecommunication%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20the%20United%20Nations'%20digital%20technology%20agency%2C%20and%20one%20of%20its%20oldest%20arms%20%E2%80%94%20is%20supporting%20organizations%20using%20technology%20to%20achieve%20the%20UN%20SDGs%20through%20its%20AI%20for%20Good%20Innovation%20Factory%20startup%20competition.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20Indian%20applicant%20%E2%80%94%20a%20startup%20called%20Bioniks%20%E2%80%94%20has%20enabled%20a%20teenager%20to%20reclaim%20the%20ability%20to%20do%20simple%20tasks%20like%20writing%20and%20getting%20dressed%20through%20the%20use%20of%20AI-powered%20prosthetics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bb248d8-2b05-4756-80af-f86360634ae5%5C%22%3EChallenges%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20powerful%20tool%20for%20achieving%20the%20UN%20SDGs%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20notable%20risks.%20Again%2C%20as%20AI%20models%20are%20largely%20developed%20by%20American%20tech%20giants%20in%20an%20industry%20already%20constrained%20by%20gender%20and%20racial%20inequality%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-racism-bias-new-inclusive-solutions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunconscious%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20major%20flaw%20of%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20Shetty%20said%20layered%20prompts%20for%20non-English%20users%2C%20human%20review%20of%20underlying%20AI%20datasets%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20indigenous%20chatbots%20are%20paramount%20to%20achieving%20Education%20Above%20All's%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20models%20are%20also%20power-intensive%2C%20making%20them%20largely%20inaccessible%20to%20the%20populations%20of%20developing%20countries.%20That's%20why%20Shetty%20urges%20AI%20companies%20to%20provide%20their%20solutions%20via%20less%20tech-heavy%20methods%2C%20like%20SMS%2C%20and%20to%20offer%20offline%20features%20so%20users%20can%20still%20access%20AI%20resources%20when%20their%20internet%20connections%20drop.%20Open-source%2C%20free-of-charge%20subscriptions%20can%20help%2C%20too%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22feb27b5e-8e3c-422f-a96c-35723fa31624%5C%22%3EAI%20as%20a%20source%20for%20good%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChallenges%20aside%2C%20Shetty%20is%20confident%20that%20AI%20can%20be%20a%20force%20for%20good%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20particularly%20around%20education.%20She%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20truly%20energized%20by%20how%20the%20global%20education%20community%20is%20leveraging%20AI%20in%20education%3A%20WhatsApp-based%20math%20tutors%20reaching%20off-grid%20learners%3B%20algorithms%20that%20optimize%20teacher%20deployment%20in%20shortage%20areas%3B%20personalized%20content%20engines%20that%20democratize%20education%3B%20chatbots%20that%20offer%20psychosocial%20support%20in%20crisis%20zones%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Shetty%20is%20clear%20that%20AI%20should%20augment%2C%20rather%20than%20displace%2C%20human%20educators.%20And%20she%20said%20the%20technology%20should%20only%20be%20used%20if%20it%20can%20solve%20challenges%20faced%20by%20humans%20and%20add%20genuine%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimply%20put%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Blet%20machines%20handle%20the%20scale%2C%20let%20humans%20handle%20the%20soul%2C%20with%20or%20without%20AI%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonprofits-ai-tools-edtech-global-inequities-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752154305000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686e7f9af748d8c055f54014%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonprofits-ai-tools-edtech-global-inequities-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nonprofits%2C%20including%20Education%20Above%20All%20and%20Tech%20To%20The%20Rescue%2C%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20address%20global%20inequities%20and%20promote%20prosperity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nicholas%20Fearn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnonprofits-ai-tools-edtech-global-inequities-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20was%20given%20a%20failing%20score%20by%20an%20online%20scanner.%20I%20still%20landed%20over%20a%20dozen%20job%20interviews%20and%20a%20job%20offer%20in%20less%20than%2090%20days%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20how.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Company%20HR%20team%20interviewing%20African%20American%20job%20candidate%20woman%2C%20reviewing%20paper%20resume%2C%20talking%20to%20applicant%20about%20career%2C%20work%20experience%2C%20professional%20skills%2C%20achievement.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686c2fe6f748d8c055f51b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERecruiter%20Jaylyn%20Jones%20received%20a%2016%25%20score%20when%20she%20ran%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20landed%20her%20over%2012%20job%20interviews%20within%20three%20months%20through%20an%20online%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20scanner%20that%20ranks%20how%20strong%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is.%3Cp%3Efizkes%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJaylyn%20Jones%20landed%20over%2012%20interviews%20without%20tailoring%20her%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20ATS%20scanners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJones%2C%20a%20recruiter%2C%20emphasizes%20showcasing%20job%20competence%20over%20keyword%20stuffing%20in%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20shared%20which%20advice%20she%20found%20least%20helpful%20when%20she%20submitted%20her%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20through%20the%20scanner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jaylyn%20Jones%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20recruiter%20based%20in%20Pittsburgh.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20job-seeking%20myths%20I've%20heard%20is%20that%20aggressive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-to-make-your-resume-is-robot-friendly-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApplicant%20Tracking%20System%20(ATS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20scanners%20will%20filter%20out%20applicants%20whose%20applications%20are%20formatted%20a%20specific%20way.%20That's%20just%20not%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20a%20recruiter%20for%20three%20years%2C%20and%20about%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20started%20hunting%20for%20a%20new%20role.%20When%20I%20was%20applying%20for%20new%20recruiting%20jobs%20in%202024%2C%20I%20took%20my%20personal%20experience%20using%20ATS%20systems%20into%20account%20and%20proved%20that%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fats-resume-how-to-build-templates-dream-job-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etailor%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20ATS%3C%2Fa%3E%20scanners%20to%20land%20a%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20I%20formatted%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20stand%20out%20among%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22615da652-d110-4d63-8cfe-fb5750d6b7be%5C%22%3EI've%20used%20ATS%20scanners%20to%20recruit%20people%20for%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20recruiting%20job%20was%20at%20JP%20Morgan%20from%202021%20to%202024%2C%20in%20which%20I%20used%20Greenhouse%2C%20a%20popular%20ATS%20system%2C%20to%20help%20streamline%20the%20recruiting%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenhouse%20rejected%20or%20flagged%20candidates%20based%20on%20straightforward%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20over%20the%20age%20of%2018%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20authorized%20to%20work%20in%20the%20US%3F%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20no%20applicants%20were%20filtered%20out%20by%20keywords%20or%20formatting.%20If%201%2C000%20people%20applied%2C%20I%20saw%201%2C000%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20manually%20search%20for%20keywords%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20look%20for%20someone%20with%20specific%20experience%2C%20but%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-your-resume-gets-rejected-job-search-bots-people-ats-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edidn't%20get%20rid%20of%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20lacked%20that%20keyword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228673bc58-1c5f-4265-b970-731252215475%5C%22%3EOn%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20I%20focused%20less%20on%20keywords%20and%20more%20on%20showing%20my%20ability%20to%20do%20the%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20bullet-by-bullet%20on%20every%20job%20description%20and%20made%20sure%20there%20was%20something%20on%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20showed%20my%20competence%20in%20that%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reviewing%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20I'd%20simply%20ask%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BWould%20a%20reasonable%20person%20look%20at%20what%20I%20have%20on%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20they%20can%20do%20this%20job%3F%26quot%3B%20My%20strategy%20worked%3B%20I%20got%20interviewed%20by%20over%2012%20companies%2C%20and%20I%20got%20hired%20to%20recruit%20at%20a%20tech%20company%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20current%20role%2C%20I%20receive%20a%20lot%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20that%20are%20filled%20with%20a%20page%20worth%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-too-long-how-to-fix-it-job-search-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekeyword%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20getting%20to%20actual%20experience.%20Once%20it%20reaches%20the%20experience%20section%2C%20that%20part%20is%20just%20as%20filled%20with%20buzzwords.%20When%20I%20see%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20like%20this%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20red%20flag.%20I%20see%20it%20as%20somebody%20who%20has%20not%20been%20given%20the%20information%20and%20tools%20to%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250021532-2f7b-45db-acb2-7f1af03fb683%5C%22%3EJobscan%20gave%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20a%20failing%20score%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20plugged%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20landed%20me%20my%20most%20recent%20job%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobscan-resume-keywords-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20Jobscan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20online%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20scanner%20that%20ranks%20how%20strong%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is%2C%20just%20to%20see%20what%20the%20platform%20would%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20critique%20I%20received%20was%20that%20I%20was%20missing%20keywords.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20scanner%20said%20something%20like