20WPP%20said%20it%20considered%20both%20internal%20and%20external%20candidates.%20Rose%20was%20a%20surprise%20appointment%20to%20most%20observers%20BI%20spoke%20to%20and%20wasn't%20on%20their%20lists%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-will-be-wpp-new-ceo-top-internal-candidates-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprobable%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20WPP%20insider%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20optimistic%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20hire%2C%20adding%20Rose%20was%20both%20a%20fresh%20face%20and%20knowledgeable%20about%20WPP%2C%20having%20sat%20on%20its%20board%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225178%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Read%2C%20CEO%20of%20WPP%20Group%2C%20the%20largest%20global%20advertising%20and%20public%20relations%20agency%2C%20poses%20for%20a%20portrait%20at%20their%20offices%20in%20London%2C%20Britain%2C%20July%2017%2C%202019.%20%20REUTERS%2FToby%20Melville%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dcd3d353afd370a0221d4c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Read%2C%20WPP's%20outgoing%20CEO%2C%20previously%20praised%20Rose%20for%20putting%20Microsoft%20on%20the%20map%20in%20the%20UK.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican-born%20Rose%20is%20a%20former%20lawyer%20who%20switched%20to%20corporate%20roles%2C%20worked%20a%20long%20stint%20at%20Disney%20before%20joining%20Microsoft%2C%20where%20she%20is%20chief%20operating%20officer%20for%20global%20enterprise.%20She%20is%20a%20dual%20UK-US%20citizen%20and%20will%20split%20her%20time%20between%20both%20countries%2C%20which%20the%20insider%20said%20was%20another%20plus%20for%20a%20company%20listed%20on%20both%20US%20and%20UK%20stock%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20tech%20background%20would%20put%20her%20in%20good%20standing%20to%20lead%20WPP%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20newer%20and%20more%20profitable%20parts%20of%20its%20offering%20to%20clients%2C%20the%20insider%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20doesn't%20come%20from%20a%20'media'%20or%20'creative'%20background%2C%20so%20won't%20see%20the%20company%20through%20that%20lens%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20WPP%20insider%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWPP%20chair%20Philip%20Jansen%20praised%20Rose's%20experience%20building%20%26quot%3Benduring%20client%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20having%20led%20multi-billion-dollar%20operations.%20At%20Microsoft%2C%20she's%20helped%20large%20enterprises%20harness%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJansen%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20her%20expertise%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20valuable%20to%20WPP%20as%20the%20industry%20navigates%20fundamental%20changes%20and%20macroeconomic%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1c677c7-7024-4b75-8886-e802f5fa1fb2%5C%22%3EA%20US%20to%20UK%20import%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20studied%20at%20Columbia%20University%20and%20New%20York%20Law%20School%20before%20relocating%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20at%20the%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Overy%20law%20firm%20in%20London%20and%20later%20joined%20Disney%20as%20legal%20counsel%20for%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIan%20Twinn%2C%20former%20director%20of%20public%20affairs%20for%20UK%20advertising%20trade%20body%20ISBA%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Rose's%20legal%20background%20would%20help%20her%20navigate%20the%20PR%20highs%20and%20lows%20of%20running%20a%20large%20public%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20being%20a%20public%20affairs%20guy%2C%20you%20do%20rely%20on%20people%20with%20a%20good%20legal%20background%20%E2%80%94%20it%20makes%20a%20big%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Twinn%2C%20who%20briefly%20interacted%20with%20Rose%20while%20she%20was%20at%20Disney.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20very%20receptive%20and%20very%20focused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22finding%20nemo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ins