20recalls%20first%20meeting%20Rose%20at%20this%20time%2C%20when%20he%20was%20UK%20country%20manager%20at%20LinkedIn%2C%20which%20Microsoft%20acquired%20in%20December%20of%20that%20year.%20They%20worked%20together%20at%20Microsoft%20for%20almost%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraff%20described%20Rose%20as%20%26quot%3Bdirect%2C%20empathetic%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20an%20ability%20to%20create%20energy%20in%20the%20teams%20around%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20doubt%20she%20will%20be%20a%20talent%20magnet%20for%20WPP%2C%26quot%3B%20Graff%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.com%2Fbusiness-money%2Ftechnology%2Farticle%2Finterview-my-job-is-to-make-customers-look-cool-says-cindy-rose-boss-of-microsoft-uk-3gt2nkfzr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERead%20previously%20credited%20Rose%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20putting%20Microsoft%20on%20the%20map%20among%20UK%20business%20leaders%20and%20politicians.%20She%20also%20championed%20diversity%2C%20both%20within%20Microsoft%20and%20in%20encouraging%20people%20from%20different%20backgrounds%20to%20take%20up%20careers%20in%20tech.%20She%20will%20be%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20be%20chief%20executive%20of%20a%20global%20advertising%20holding%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221820f534-cdaa-4b2f-98e4-135041084d4e%5C%22%3EBringing%20a%20touch%20of%20Microsoft%20to%20WPP%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American-accented%20Rose%20was%20made%20an%20Officer%20of%20the%20British%20Empire%2C%20an%20honor%20conferred%20by%20the%20UK%20government%2C%20and%20received%20it%20from%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20in%202019.%20Rose%20was%20promoted%20to%20become%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20in%20Western%20Europe%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20rose%20to%20her%20most%20recent%20position%20in%202023.%20In%20this%20role%2C%20she%20was%20responsible%20for%20helping%20huge%20blue-chip%20businesses%20understand%20and%20use%20technologies%20like%20AI%20to%20transform%20their%2