C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20I'm%20still%20cheaper%20than%20dirt.%20If%20our%20family%20goes%20out%20to%20dinner%2C%20we%20drink%20water%20or%20get%20one%20soda%20to%20share.%20My%2016-year-old%20got%20a%20hand-me-down%20car%20when%20he%20got%20his%20license%3A%20a%202014%20Nissan%20Rogue.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20like%20the%20millionaire%20next%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20life%2C%20I've%20learned%20more%20from%20my%20failures%20than%20I%20have%20from%20my%20successes.%20If%20my%20show%20hadn't%20been%20canceled%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20started%20making%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20my%20sons%20to%20experience%20failure%2C%20but%20I'm%20worried%20that%20they're%20part%20of%20a%20generation%20that%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20fail%20well.%20I%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20experience%20serious%20failures%2C%20like%20mental%20health%20issues%20or%20financial%20scams.%20But%20if%20they%20don't%20make%20the%20sports%20team%2C%20I'm%20not%20the%20parent%20calling%20the%20school%20to%20express%20outrage.%20Failure%20is%20our%20friend%20in%20finances%2C%20romance%2C%20and%20life.%20It's%20where%20we%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreated-two-top-performing-qvc-brands-while-parenting-boys-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752145621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686270b9f748d8c055f49ec8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreated-two-top-performing-qvc-brands-while-parenting-boys-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kim%20Gravel%20went%20from%20being%20a%20pageant%20winner%20to%20an%20entrepreneur.%20She%20has%20two%20teens%20and%20wants%20them%20to%20experience%20failure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreated-two-top-perfo