%20Mewar%20region%2C%20and%20because%20of%20the%20availability%20of%20fresh%20water%2C%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20dishes%20that%20include%20fish.%20But%20because%20it%20does%20not%20fit%20into%20the%20homogenous%20idea%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20all%20this%20is%20often%20excluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20curated%20dining%20experiences%20and%20pop-up%20events%2C%20Dipali%20brings%20out%20these%20underrated%20aspects%20of%20Rajasthani%20cuisine.%20She%20introduces%20these%20dishes%20to%20a%20wider%20audience%20and%20helps%20them%20develop%20a%20deeper%20connection%20to%20the%20food%20they%E2%80%99re%20enjoying%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20thorough%20understanding%20of%20its%20origins%20and%20cultural%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEncouraging%20children%20to%20document%20their%20family%20recipes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20core%20principles%20of%20%E2%80%98The%20Kindness%20Meal%E2%80%99%20is%20generational%20sharing%2C%20where%20older%20generations%20pass%20down%20their%20knowledge%20of%20food%20and%20recipes%20to%20younger%20people.%20This%20is%20crucial%20in%20a%20time%20when%20traditional%20recipes%20are%20being%20lost%20due%20to%20the%20changing%20dynamics%20of%20family%20structures%20and%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20organise%20%E2%80%98Food%20Culture%20Play%20Dates%E2%80%99%20for%20children%20aged%20between%20seven%20and%2014%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20teach%20children%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20food%20in%20their%20cultural%20heritage.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20train%20the%20kids%20to%20be%20ethnographic%20and%20document%20their%20family%20recipes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dipali%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20creates%20this%20sense%20of%20wonder%20%E2%80%94%20what%20was%20the%20food%2C%20and%20where%20is%20it%20coming%20from%3F%20And%20makes%20you%20want%20to%20know%20more.%E2%80%9D%20The%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20family%20members%20about%20the%20food%20they%20ate%20growing%20up%20and%20the%20stories%20around%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20broadly%20identifies%20nine%20cultural%20zones%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20geography%2C%20the%20agricultural%20features%2C%20and%20language.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-62-1752055399-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-466528%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20broadly%20identifies%20nine%20cultural%20zones%20in%20Rajasthan%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20geography%2C%20the%20agricultural%20features%2C%20and%20language%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipali%20recalls%20a%20heartwarming%20tale%20from%20one%20of%20their%20sessions%2C%20where%20a%20child%20shared%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20family%E2%80%99s%20tradition%20of%20drinking%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ejadi%20ber%20ki%20chai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20tea%20made%20from%20the%20dried%20fruit%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eber%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Etree%2C%20to%20help%20her%20grandmother%20with%20insomnia.%20The%20child%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20incredibly%20moved%2