0all%20begins%20to%20look%20and%20taste%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%20By%20documenting%20and%20sharing%20these%20recipes%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Kindness%20Meal%E2%80%99%20is%20helping%20future%20generations%20not%20lose%20touch%20with%20their%20culinary%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20people%20connect%20to%20their%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManohar%20Kabeer%20(32)%2C%20a%20communications%20professional%2C%20found%20out%20about%20%E2%80%98The%20Kindness%20Meal%E2%80%99%20when%20a%20friend%20shared%20a%20reel%20of%20theirs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20as%20though%20I%20was%20the%20beneficiary%20of%20what%20she%20was%20trying%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20A%20Rajasthani%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Manohar%20was%20taken%20back%20to%20summers%20in%20his%C2%A0%3Cem%3Enani%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%20house.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20would%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20dishes%20made%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(pearl%20millets)%2C%20I%20especially%20remember%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Erabdi%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20thickened%2C%20sweetened%20milk%20dish).%20Then%20there%20were%20foraged%20foods%20like%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emangodi%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20variation%20of%20the%20mung%20bean)%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esangri%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(desert%20bean)%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20would%20be%20used%20to%20make%20sabzi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-63-1752055497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20documenting%20and%20sharing%20these%20recipes%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Kindness%20Meal%E2%80%99%20is%20helping%20future%20generations%20not%20lose%20touch%20with%20their%20culinary%20heritage..%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa