s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20space%20to%20learn%2C%20earn%2C%20and%20be%20seen%20on%20their%20own%20terms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20in%20Kaushalya%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20women%20like%20her%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20a%20place%20with%20tight%20rules%20or%20fixed%20outcomes.%20It%20happened%20in%20a%20space%20where%20women%20set%20the%20pace%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20flexibility%20is%20by%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Geetanjali%20Chopra%2C%20founder%20of%20Wishes%20and%20Blessings%2C%20the%20organisation%20behind%20the%20SAHAS%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20rigid%20rules%20or%20targets.%20The%20women%20can%20bring%20their%20children%2C%20take%20breaks%2C%20and%20take%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time.%20For%20many%20of%20them%2C%20this%20is%20their%20first%20experience%20of%20being%20in%20a%20learning%20environment%20without%20judgement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20homes%20across%20India%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives%20are%20tied%20to%20routines%20and%20expectations%20set%20by%20others.%20The%20idea%20that%20they%20can%20step%20into%20a%20space%20where%20their%20time%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20progress%20are%20fully%20respected%20is%20still%20rare.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20this%20centre%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20stitching%20programme%20has%20quietly%20become%20something%20more.%20Women%20show%20up%20not%20just%20to%20work%2C%20but%20to%20build%20a%20community.%20They%20bring%20their%20children%20along%2C%20learn%20the%20alphabet%2C%20share%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20teach%20each%20other%20stitching%20tricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-08T172640.677-17