d%20this%20is%20essentially%20the%20message%20that%20the%20architects%20have%20attempted%20to%20convey%2C%20the%20freedom%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Malik%20details%20the%20restoration%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20evident%3A%20the%20rendering%20was%20rooted%20in%20honest%20appreciation%20of%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20history.%20The%20end%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20aesthetics%2C%20but%20to%20preserve%20the%20antiquity%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20involved%20repurposing%20the%20Burma%20Teak%20that%20was%20found%20under%20the%20plaster%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-53-1751977084-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-465918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EA%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20Ambico%20Ice%20Factory%20involved%20repurposing%20the%20Burma%20Teak%20that%20was%20found%20under%20the%20plaster%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20